{"tid":1606170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來烏克蘭有個團體一直都好支持我哋","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:20:58.000Z","uid":57433,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc84e02d382294d100fb886f33971371b805082","tid":1606170,"uid":57433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"事源： 香港人睇winter on fire 咁雄心壯志<br />\n929AntiChinaziProtest 其實烏克蘭基輔 係有集會<br />\n但係可惜好少香港人follow 好少香港人有關注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家 烏克蘭係有個好後生嘅團體好支持香港人 <br />\n佢個名叫：Liberal Democratic League of Ukraine<br />\n<br />\nIg page: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/ldlu_official?igshid=1tp73vyh8vk4h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fldlu_official%3Figshid%3D1tp73vyh8vk4h&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=67e7bf40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/ldlu_official?igshid=1tp73vyh8vk4h</a><br />\n<br />\nFb page: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/libdemleague/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flibdemleague%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=2777eb88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/libdemleague/</a><br />\n<br />\n929fb page: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/ufhkc/?ref=m_notif&amp;notif_t=page_highlights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fufhkc%2F%3Fref%3Dm_notif%26notif_t%3Dpage_highlights&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=da5f842f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/ufhkc/?ref=m_notif&amp;notif_t=page_highlights</a><br />\n<br />\n你睇番佢今次 真係有支持我地㗎！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdDmwym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDdDmwym.png&h=15227d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrB3KTn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrB3KTn.png&h=51184e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsn20rJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffsn20rJ.png&h=e49c9296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋人地14年 已經支持緊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVk8bCq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVk8bCq.png&h=0c80991f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/ufhkc/photos/a.477775869238707/951855911830698/?type=3&amp;source=48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fufhkc%2Fphotos%2Fa.477775869238707%2F951855911830698%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D48&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=c528dfb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/ufhkc/photos/a.477775869238707/951855911830698/?type=3&amp;source=48</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJxDhu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJxDhu.png&h=bba1641d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=772836289424704&amp;id=100000950192649&amp;set=a.310742245634113&amp;source=48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D772836289424704%26id%3D100000950192649%26set%3Da.310742245634113%26source%3D48&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6sg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=844834fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=772836289424704&amp;id=100000950192649&amp;set=a.310742245634113&amp;source=48</a><br />\n<br />\n大家支持吓佢地啦<br />\nGlory to Ukraine <br />\nGlory to Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n最後，賀佢老母"},{"pid":"39264481dd11a9be805d0ab97a8803299084baa6","tid":1606170,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"十一特別版，習總連儂地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606161</a><br />\n- 分享自 L